      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2003-07-09</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-02-24T19:52:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>State Regulation of Marriage Is Appropriate Act - Amends Federal law to repeal the statutory definition of "marriage" as meaning only a legal union between one man and one woman as husband and wife, and of "spouse" as referring only to a person of the opposite sex who is a husband or a wife.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
